===Definitions===
{{head|zh|hanzi}}

# [[pleased]]; [[happy]]
#: {{syn|zh|樂<tr:lè>}}
#: {{zh-x|快感|pleasure}}
#: {{zh-x|大快人心|to the great satisfaction of the people}}
# [[forthright]]; [[plainspoken]]
#: {{zh-x|心直口快|frank and outspoken}}
# [[rapid]]; [[quick]]; [[speedy]]; [[fast]]
#: {{syn|zh|速}}
