#: {{zh-x|腦子 快|quick-witted}}
# [[quickly]]; [[hurriedly]]
#: {{zh-x|快 來 幫忙！|Come and help quickly!}}
# to be [[about]] to; [[almost]]
#: {{zh-x|我 快 到 了。|I am '''about to''' arrive.}}
#: {{zh-x|快 八點 了。|It's almost 8.}}
# {{lb|zh|of [[time zone]]s}} to be [[ahead]] of
#: {{ant|zh|慢}}
